**Title**:       Character Pattern Analysis of Political Discourse: Differentiating Speaker Signatures Across Ideological and Era Divides
**Subtitle**:    An Application of the Character Assessment Framework (CAF) v6.1 to a Diverse Corpus of American Political Speech

